query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT clienteId) as clientes_com_cte FROM cte_notas; SELECT COUNT(*) as total_nsu, COUNT(CASE WHEN ultimoNsu > 0 THEN 1 END) as nsu_positivo FROM cte_nsu_control; SELECT contabilidadeId, COUNT(*) as total FROM cte_nsu_control GROUP BY contabilidadeId;
